headline: Hologic Expands Panther Fusion's Menu With Diagnostic Innovation
summary: HOLX expands its Panther Fusion platform with new GI bacterial assays, securing FDA and EU approvals to boost Diagnostics growth.

headline: 3 Reasons HOLX is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: While the S&P 500 is up 34.7% since April 2025, Hologic (currently trading at $67.73 per share) has lagged behind, posting a return of 15.9%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
